text: Ivanovsky () is a rural locality (a settlement) in Nachalovsky Selsoviet, Privolzhsky District, Astrakhan Oblast, Russia. The population was 63 as of 2010. There are 10 streets. == Geography == It is located 20 km from Astrakhan, 7 km from Nachalovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Privolzhsky District, Astrakhan Oblast
title: Ivanovsky, Astrakhan Oblast
